{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"db34eb22c4","title":"毛泽东第一次接见红卫兵时在天安门上同彭小蒙的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d16f16a0f9","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"db34eb22c4"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"de13de531e","type":"title","text":"第一次接见红卫兵时在天安门上同彭小蒙的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"6c101b1f69","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"6322eac1b9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：陆平现在干什么？","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"0ff26d01de","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：陆平在北大扫地。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"72aab42e34","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：陆平只能扫地，就象我一样，我到了你们学校也只能扫扫地，别的干不来。我是你们的勤务员。张承先也是个坏人，把你们“红旗”拆散了。你们要把“红旗”拉起来。你们发展了多少人呢？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"5e8668629b","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：有发展了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"6449b47a86","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这就对头了。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"dbb6382011","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：主席身体好不好？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"2c4ae88a89","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我身体很好。我在长江里游泳，有个青年同志肝痛了，我就上来了，要不然可以游三、四个小时。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"14ae69d474","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：下一步怎么办？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"2d3c16498d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们一斗二批三改，按十六条办事。会不会游泳？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"67bdaba81e","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：才学会，游得不好，很乱。只会游十几米。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"fb8445720d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那不叫游泳，那叫闲庭信步。（这时毛作了闲庭信步的样子）你要能这样，就从必然王国到自由王国了。你们老怕别人批评。马克思主义就是压出来的。经风雨，发展兴旺起来。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"88d07db713","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不能让她老出风头，要让她谦虚。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"},{"id":"464eb5aa1d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你怎么能这样说呢？要让人家干革命嘛！","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4"}],"page":{"id":"cf674b7393","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"db34eb22c4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}